divs: Sighting Detailsa late summer evening in september in northern minnesota in 1979 i was riding my bike and all of a sudden i looked up and i was right under this thing it was hovering over the tree line it was a hase green and while i was under it it shot a haze green light in my eyes it was documented by a doctor there was something wrong with my eyes but they could not say what it was . well thats all i canh really say on here thank you again and god bless
Summary: i was riding my bike as a young teen in early fall and just after dark i rode my bike under it and it flashed a haze green light in my eyes
